{"tid":606903,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[樓本位] 央行漸棄美元改以房貸發行人民幣","createTime":"2018-03-27T00:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T01:09:22.000Z","uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ced2224f9e50e69e3bc13552cad544763b4de701","tid":606903,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"【人民幣漸跟美元分手之後....】<br />\n【「房價將綁架貨幣、綁架匯率、綁架整個中國。」】<br />\n<br />\n過去廿幾年，八成人民幣的發行，是靠出口企業賺取美金，這筆美元存到內地金融機構，稱為外匯佔款。金融機構再把美元換成人民幣，去年這個數額就有21萬億，即是人民幣的基礎價值就是來自美元<br />\n<br />\n但是自2013年開始，美元的外匯佔款開始逐年減少，人民幣供應隨之變得緊張，當年就出現錢荒。<br />\n<br />\n【央行漸棄美元改以房貸發行人民幣】<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行想到了另一種方法製造貨幣供應，就是由央行以各種方式，直接借款給金融機構，再以放貸形式製造人民幣供應。<br />\n<br />\n以這種方式發行貨幣的比例，由2013年的4.1%，急升至去年的28.2%，而美元的外匯佔款比例，就由83%跌至59.2%。<br />\n<br />\n再看貸款組成，居民貸款過去三年已超過企業貸款，成為主要貸款類別，當中九成都是借錢來買樓。<br />\n<br />\n【人民幣信用依賴房地產市場】<br />\n<br />\n有關注內地經濟的網絡作家「老蠻」這樣總結目前的形勢:<br />\n「到了2017年末，房地產不光是綁架了經濟，它還綁架了貨幣、綁架了匯率、綁架了整個中國。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果2018年房地產市場發生萎縮，商業銀行拿了央行的錢放貸放不出去，那就意味著連印錢都印不出來了，整個經濟活動瞬間就會陷入資金緊縮局面，錢荒立刻發作。而喪失了房價的支撐，喪失了房價的信用背書，人民幣匯率當場就會被打入冰點。」<br />\n<br />\n#人民幣匯價<br />\n#外匯儲備<br />\n#房地產<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"103b533b0ce5838137fcdd215c03ed9c641e13ea","tid":606903,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:45:36.000Z","msg":"香港可唔可以房貸發行港幣？"},{"pid":"c3f8d649e094ccfc932e46d0868c5965e6ab8634","tid":606903,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"距離支爆又近一步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8bca0463022b4b617b2a1374eb809ce52081d","tid":606903,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"明明自己無外匯就話自己棄美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678c42c5404ec4d51cf827f4e346189aa5485f50","tid":606903,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3f8d649e094ccfc932e46d0868c5965e6ab8634","tid":606903,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:47:53.000Z","msg":"距離支爆又近一步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"唔怪得可以拋售美債<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c4dc4d1842e59f08e3c8d2989ab455a8fadd2f","tid":606903,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e8bca0463022b4b617b2a1374eb809ce52081d","tid":606903,"uid":44171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"明明自己無外匯就話自己棄美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"有一半外匯係外資放入 實際上冇咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有種佢私有晒 果時我諗引起外國玩到佢傻"},{"pid":"bea784dfb2c87fd3d555bea1e21e029468e727aa","tid":606903,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:03:02.000Z","msg":"鬼城抵押？"},{"pid":"a25647b39455faf2cf62a48cbdbca7b545e3c028","tid":606903,"uid":4503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:06:11.000Z","msg":"次按 翻版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後包裝好又可以按多次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換錢"},{"pid":"b03affb4c6a4d50dbf6724e750317a35c96bfa14","tid":606903,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103b533b0ce5838137fcdd215c03ed9